@host = http://localhost:2607

### Health check
GET {{host}}/

### List all bookmarks
GET {{host}}/bookmarks

### Get one bookmark
GET {{host}}/bookmarks/1

### Create a bookmark
POST {{host}}/bookmarks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://github.com",
  "title": "GitHub"
}

### Update a bookmark
PUT {{host}}/bookmarks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://nodejs.org",
  "title": "Node.js (updated)"
}

### Delete a bookmark
DELETE {{host}}/bookmarks/1

### --- error cases ---

### Missing url (400)
POST {{host}}/bookmarks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "no url here"
}

### Non-existent id (404)
GET {{host}}/bookmarks/9999

### Invalid id (400)
GET {{host}}/bookmarks/abc
